WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.902 --> 00:00:03.570
WHAT TABLE YOU GUYS
SIT AT?

00:00:03.604 --> 00:00:06.740
- JEFF WAS A REFEREE
IN THE NBA.

00:00:06.773 --> 00:00:09.476
- EXACTLY, THAT'S A CARRY.
WE'RE GOING THAT WAY.

00:00:09.510 --> 00:00:13.480
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

00:00:13.514 --> 00:00:16.517
WE DOING HANDS IN PANTS?
IS THAT WHAT WE'RE DOING?

00:00:16.550 --> 00:00:19.386
LOVE THE KID 'N PLAY MOVIES.
I LOVE THOSE KID 'N PLAY MOVIES.

00:00:19.419 --> 00:00:22.289
THOSE GUYS? SHOO.
THEY EVER BEEN IN HERE?

00:00:22.322 --> 00:00:23.891
YOU GUYS LIKE A DUO?

00:00:23.924 --> 00:00:25.993
YOU LOOKING FOR
THREE MUSKETEERS OR ANYTHING?

00:00:29.096 --> 00:00:30.697
TWO-TO-ONE SAYS I SIT
WITH YOU GUYS

00:00:30.731 --> 00:00:32.266
AND IT'S TATER TOTS
FOR LUNCH.

00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:37.337
HEY, CROSBY, STILLS,
YOU LOOKING FOR A NASH?

00:00:37.371 --> 00:00:39.373
RIGHT.

00:00:39.406 --> 00:00:41.675
- WITH NOWHERE TO SIT...
- YOU GUYS HANGING? NO?

00:00:41.708 --> 00:00:44.378
- JEFF NEEDS
TO ASSERT HIMSELF...

00:00:44.411 --> 00:00:45.979
- [drops tray on table]

00:00:46.013 --> 00:00:47.948
- OR RISK BECOMING A TARGET.

00:00:47.981 --> 00:00:49.283
- [blows whistle]

00:00:52.753 --> 00:00:54.655
FINE!

00:00:54.688 --> 00:00:56.423
I'LL BE YOUR ENEMY!

00:00:56.456 --> 00:00:59.293
BUT THE THING I'LL YOU
IS I WILL BE DOWNSTAIRS

00:00:59.326 --> 00:01:01.461
IN THE TV ROOM
THIS AFTERNOON,

00:01:01.495 --> 00:01:05.365
AND YOU CAN DO WHATEVER YOU WANT
AT THAT POINT.

00:01:05.399 --> 00:01:07.568
YOU COULD THINK
ABOUT YOUR GIRLFRIEND AT HOME.

00:01:07.601 --> 00:01:11.305
YOU WANT IT TO BE SWEET?
SOUTHERN BELLE?

00:01:11.338 --> 00:01:13.340
[soft voice]
WELL, I NEVER!

00:01:13.373 --> 00:01:15.275
[normal voice]
I'LL DO THAT ALL DAY.

00:01:15.309 --> 00:01:17.544
BUT YOU GOTTA COME DOWN
TO THE TV ROOM,

00:01:17.578 --> 00:01:18.879
'CAUSE I'M NOT
COMING TO YOU.

00:01:18.912 --> 00:01:20.480
UNLESS YOU WANT ME
TO COME TO YOU, I WILL.

00:01:20.514 --> 00:01:22.549
YEAH, I'M NOT SURE IF I'M GONNA
BE A TOP OR A BOTTOM.

00:01:22.583 --> 00:01:25.652
I GUESS I'LL, YOU KNOW,
WHEN--WHEN THE GUYS SHOW UP.

00:01:25.686 --> 00:01:28.755
- NO ONE ACCEPTS
JEFF'S INVITATION.

00:01:28.789 --> 00:01:30.824
- SEEMS LIKE SOME OF THE GUYS
IN THE YARD

00:01:30.858 --> 00:01:32.726
ARE GIVING ME
THE COLD SHOULDER, BUT--

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:34.161
[louder] SEEMS LIKE SOME OF
OF THE GUYS IN THE YARD

00:01:34.194 --> 00:01:35.596
ARE GIVING ME
THE COLD SHOULDER.

00:01:35.629 --> 00:01:38.298
- YOU'LL GET THROUGH IT.
I DID.

00:01:38.332 --> 00:01:40.400
- [chuckles]

00:01:40.434 --> 00:01:43.303
OH, IT'S GOOD TO HAVE
A FRIEND.

00:01:43.337 --> 00:01:45.506
- MORE OF A CELLMATE.
- YEAH.

00:01:45.539 --> 00:01:46.974
CELLMATES DON'T TALK
LIKE THIS.

00:01:47.007 --> 00:01:48.876
- I'M OUT IN A MONTH.

00:01:48.909 --> 00:01:51.144
I CAN'T WAIT TO SEE
MY BEAUTIFUL GIRLS.

00:01:51.178 --> 00:01:54.781
- YOU'RE A FAM--UNH.
[defecating]

00:01:54.815 --> 00:01:56.950
YOU'RE A FAMILY MAN, HUH?

00:01:56.984 --> 00:01:59.753
[toilet flushes]

00:01:59.786 --> 00:02:02.122
FOR THE REST OF MY LIFE,
IT'S LIKE I'VE BEEN IN SOLITARY,

00:02:02.155 --> 00:02:03.924
AND ALL OF A SUDDEN,
YOU KNOW,

00:02:03.957 --> 00:02:05.626
I GOT A GROUP OF GUYS
THAT I CAN CONNECT WITH.

00:02:05.659 --> 00:02:08.462
WE'RE LOCKED IN HERE TOGETHER.
THERE'S NO ESCAPING.

00:02:10.864 --> 00:02:13.534
MAURICE, I HAD A DREAM
THAT YOU WOULDN'T BELIEVE.

00:02:13.567 --> 00:02:15.169
I GUESS I'LL HAVE TO TELL YOU
THE WHOLE THING

